devdoc.details: Manages battle predictions, results, and player statistics

emergencyWithdraw().details: Emergency function to withdraw funds (if any)

getAccuracy(address).details: Get accuracy percentage for a player

returns._0: BattleRecord struct for the specified battle

getBattleCount().details: Get total number of battles recorded

getPlayerBattleCount(address).details: Get number of battles for a player

getPlayerBattleIds(address).details: Get all battle IDs for a player

getUserStats(address).details: Get complete statistics for a player

submitBattle(string,string,string,string.details: Submit a battle result and update player statistics

returns._0: battleId The ID of the recorded battle
returns._1: wasCorrect Whether the prediction was correct
returns._2: totalPointsEarned Points earned from this battle

wasPredictionCorrect(uint256,address).details: Compare if a player's prediction was correct

returns._0: bool Whether the prediction was correct
